  "detailed_description": "Our hero decided to escape from the hustle and bustle of the city and get out into nature to relax in a cabin that was in the mountains. <br />\r\nAmazing sunsets, fresh air, the tranquility of the mountains, but then a sandstorm started. His car broke down, the dust robbed him of any hope of getting his car repaired... <br />\r\nHe didn't encounter a single soul while he waited for the dust storm to end. Was there an abandoned building nearby, or did it only appear abandoned? <br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeatures: <br />\r\n-High quality graphics <br />\r\n-Tense atmosphere of fear <br />\r\n-High quality audio support. <br />\r\n-Simple but enjoyable gameplay.",
